UNCRUSTIFY

1. copy uncrustify binary in the folders specfied by PATH variable

2. create a link to uncrustify-vimrc as ~/.uncrustify-vimrc

3. Source this file in your ~/.vimrc.after
  For Example look at vimrc.after.anoop

4. for C function comments copy the func-comments.txt file in the
  same directory as uncrustify.cfg file

